The '''Comet Casino''' was a run-down [[Casino/Legends|casino]] that was located on the [[Smuggler/Legends|Smugglers]]' [[Moon/Legends|Moon]], [[Nar Shaddaa/Legends|Nar Shaddaa]]. It could be found within the [[Corellian Sector (Nar Shaddaa)/Legends|Corellian sector]] of the lunar [[Ecumenopolis/Legends|ecumenopolis]]. In [[5 BBY/Legends|5 BBY]] [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] visited the place when he searched for his old friend [[Mako Spince]] on the Smugglers' Moon.

